column2: (let* ((a (copy-sequence "x")) (b (copy-sequence "x")) (ht (make-hash-table :test 'eq :size 5))) (setf (gethash a ht) 'a) (setf (gethash b ht) 'b) (let* ((entries (apply #'append (internal--hash-table-buckets ht))) (keys (mapcar #'car entries)) (hashes (mapcar #'cdr entries))) (list (hash-table-count ht) (length entries) (not (memq nil keys)) (not (= (car hashes) (cadr hashes))) (gethash a ht 'miss) (gethash b ht 'miss))))
